<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 rén de shēng mìng zhǐ yī cì zài shēng mìng zhōng hé zhǔ xiāng yù,
 cóng cǐ hé zhǔ yǒng bù fēn lí yī shēng yuàn yì hé zhǔ yuǎn qù,
 wǒ zài mǔ fù zhōng, tā zǎo yǐ kàn jiàn wǒ zài mǔ fù zhōng zhǔ zǎo yǐ jiǎn xuǎn
 cóng zuì kǔ de rì zi zǒu dào jīn tiān, yī qiè dōu shì shén de ēn diǎn,
 wǒ men yī tóng zhàn zài shén de diàn, dōu jìn bù zhù xiǎng qǐ cóng qián,
 yuàn qǐ chū nà kē huǒ rè de xīn, néng chí shǒu dào yǒng yǒng yuǎn yuǎn.</lyrics>
<title>rén de shēng mìng zhǐ yǒu yī cì 迦南318</title>
